title: Pixies live bootleg 1991 "Gone To Heaven" FM broadcast MP3
description:
Like my other three torrents, this is another one I haven&#039;t created myself, but downloaded from dimeadozen

Specifically, here: http://www.dimeadozen.org/torrents-details.php?id=164091


I&#039;m all about giving credit and shit like that


Anyway, this looks like a damn good show, with some songs I&#039;ve been looking for live versions of for a while (Alec-fucking-Eiffel!...Dancing The Manta Ray...Lovely Day...Good shit)

I say "shit" far too much


Having listened to some of it now, it&#039;s absolutely incredible, and Eric Drew Feldman accompanies them on keyboards, so stuff like Alec Eiffel, Motorway to Roswell and Velouria sounds better


This would have been perfect if they&#039;d played Planet of Sound, but at least they didn&#039;t play fucking Head On (nothing much against that song, but it&#039;s the weakest song on Trompe le Monde)


Enjoy
